Test Passed:
  users:
%v
  move: %v
  =>
  expected battle pieces:
%v
  actual battle pieces:
%v
`,
				formatSlice(test.users),
				test.mv,
				formatSlice(test.expectedFightLocations),
				formatSlice(output),
